(<span class="type"><abbr title="Portable Document Format">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class="file-size">231KB</span>, <span class="page-length">5 pages</span>)
</span></p>
  </li>
  <li><a rel="external" href="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/796017/form-phar3b-appendix.pdf">hosts of xylella fastidiosa that require a plant passport for all wholesale movement</a></li>
  <li><span id="attachment_3347189" class="attachment-inline">
